{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"92663ce236","title":"中央文革小组关于《广西日报》事件的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"98ec94531f","index":0,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":30,"articleId":"92663ce236","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"新闻广播和出版","id":"268718f23b","type":"主题"},{"name":"军队和军事","id":"6f7a683373","type":"主题"},{"name":"中共中央电报","id":"b4f67da172","type":"发行机构"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"通讯","id":"d5cbd05390","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"中央文件","id":"ef6e778547","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8ae1eab1a7","type":"title","text":"中央文革小组关于《广西日报》事件的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"92663ce236","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eddf631278","type":"paragraph","text":"广西军区并请转抄印给驻《广西日报》和在报社前静坐的“八·三一广西红卫兵”总部、北京驻邕的革命同志们：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"92663ce236","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"036421b90b","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）进驻报社的同学们，你们立即退出报社，在报社门前静坐的同学们，你们立即退出报社，保证报纸正常出版，否则对当前批判党内最大的走资本主义道路的当权派不利。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"92663ce236","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"90f77425d6","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）要维护军管小组、革命组织，要支持军队对报社军管工作，军管小组成员要做必要的调整。组织版面小组吸收革命组织代表参加，协助军管搞好报纸。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"92663ce236","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f5ba1824c1","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）有意见可以和军管小组商量解决，不要采取静坐，强拉军管小组辩论的方法，应保持军管小组正常工作。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"92663ce236","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c3be014e05","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）对某篇文章有意见，可以进行批判，也可以在报上讨论。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"92663ce236","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"71043b6d88","type":"paragraph","text":"中央文革","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"92663ce236","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d752085a75","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年四月三十日","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"92663ce236","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}